    ModelElement, RefreshableDialog, UndoListener, java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.util.EventListener, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.event.UndoableEditListener
    public final class ValidationDisplayPanel
extends DockablePanel
implements UndoListener, javax.swing.event.UndoableEditListener, RefreshableDialog
    The main component of the Validation Display. This panel is intended to display the ASCII export of a model and the validation output from the analysis code's verification process (if available).
